Vladimir Loukonine, Anatoli Ivanov, &quot;Persian Miniatures&quot;
ISBN: 1844847829 | 2010 | PDF | 256 pages | 46 MB

Encounter one of history's greatest civilisations through miniatures. In Persian Miniatures, the story of the magnificent Persian Empire is told by way of a small but vibrant artistic tradition. The colourful images, which are, in fact, elaborate book illustrations, introduce a curious world of adventures, heroes and sovereigns. The layout highlights three details from each image and helps to discover amazing peculiarities.
